00:17:33.870 --> 00:17:36.310
But our goal is to
continue to open up

00:17:36.310 --> 00:17:39.220
more and more of the things
that can be edited on the map,

00:17:39.220 --> 00:17:42.550
so that individual users
can actually tell us

00:17:42.550 --> 00:17:47.322
about things that are wrong.

00:17:47.322 --> 00:17:49.920
BRANDI: And you said that
one of your first things you

00:17:49.920 --> 00:17:51.420
