00:18:01.540 --> 00:18:03.300
I try to be pretty
well-documented.

00:18:03.300 --> 00:18:05.440
And I don't have
that in my notes.

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:09.390
I know that it's kind
of come full circle.

00:18:09.390 --> 00:18:11.160
And that's been the
most fulfilling part

00:18:11.160 --> 00:18:13.290
of this whole process that
I've been involved with,

00:18:13.290 --> 00:18:16.080
in that I first saw the
name on Google Maps.

00:18:16.080 --> 00:18:18.330
And you go through
an 18-month period

00:18:18.330 --> 00:18:21.990
of figuring out who to talk
to, following up, following up,

00:18:21.990 --> 00:18:23.520
waiting, being
patient, having to go

00:18:23.520 --> 00:18:25.410
through the bureaucratic steps.

00:18:25.410 --> 00:18:29.820
And then it truly was that
I was very happy when I saw

00:18:29.820 --> 00:18:32.400
the board approved the name.

00:18:32.400 --> 00:18:34.680
But I was the most
satisfied when

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:36.880
I saw the update
happen on Google Maps.

00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:41.160
It was just that recognition
that in modern day,

00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:43.050
it's not the paper map,
it's the digital map.

00:18:43.050 --> 00:18:44.010
That's what people see.

00:18:44.010 --> 00:18:46.175
There are more
people seeing maps,

00:18:46.175 --> 00:18:48.300
because they have smartphones,
they have computers.

00:18:48.300 --> 00:18:51.150
They simply have more
access to the information.

00:18:51.150 --> 00:18:53.264
And that information
is, quite frankly,

00:18:53.264 --> 00:18:54.930
for most people are
going to be digital.

00:18:54.930 --> 00:18:59.667
So it may take 5, 10
years for paper maps

00:18:59.667 --> 00:19:00.750
in the area to be updated.

00:19:00.750 --> 00:19:03.080
It may take another 10 or 20
years for books to be updated.

00:19:03.080 --> 00:19:04.580
It might even take
a full generation

00:19:04.580 --> 00:19:08.040
before the people who
live in that area change

00:19:08.040 --> 00:19:11.220
the name they use colloquially.

00:19:11.220 --> 00:19:13.620
But for Google Maps, it
happened in 24 hours.

00:19:13.620 --> 00:19:15.750
And the impact of
that has the potential

00:19:15.750 --> 00:19:17.430
to reach millions of people.

00:19:17.430 --> 00:19:19.500
And so that's probably
the most proud

00:19:19.500 --> 00:19:22.860
that I am of this whole process,
is that so many more people

00:19:22.860 --> 00:19:26.250
have access to this new name.

00:19:26.250 --> 00:19:29.010
And it gives so much more
weight to the power that we all

00:19:29.010 --> 00:19:31.800
have to be able to change
names, to change things

00:19:31.800 --> 00:19:35.381
that we see as being wrong, and
standing up and saying, hey,

00:19:35.381 --> 00:19:37.380
this is absolutely not
right, this is offensive,

00:19:37.380 --> 00:19:38.820
this is derogatory.

00:19:38.820 --> 00:19:40.320
Maybe not to me
personally, but it's

00:19:40.320 --> 00:19:42.420
derogatory to
someone that I know

00:19:42.420 --> 00:19:44.704
or someone that I could
know or just in general.

00:19:44.704 --> 00:19:46.620
So there is that ability
to change it and have

00:19:46.620 --> 00:19:47.790
it reach all those people.

00:19:47.790 --> 00:19:51.435
It's just-- it's
pretty incredible.

00:19:51.435 --> 00:19:54.620
BRANDI: So what are
you doing to change

00:19:54.620 --> 00:19:56.630
