What would you suggest
their first steps be?

00:21:10.080 --> 00:21:11.420
Or how can they help you?

00:21:11.420 --> 00:21:13.740
And what are your next
steps going to be?

00:21:13.740 --> 00:21:15.980
MAURICE TURNER: Well,
this was a big next step--

00:21:15.980 --> 00:21:17.820
