and sharing my story.

00:21:17.820 --> 00:21:21.200
So I appreciate you inviting
me to the Google Campus

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:24.770
and for all of you coming
out and all of you,

00:21:24.770 --> 00:21:26.900
wherever you are
in your offices,

00:21:26.900 --> 00:21:29.820
hearing firsthand
what I went through.

