10 minutes to learn

00:21:36.410 --> 00:21:40.170
a little bit about the name and
propose a better alternative.

00:21:40.170 --> 00:21:42.560
So that way, the
process can start.

00:21:42.560 --> 00:21:46.510
And I'm hoping that once
that decision is made,

00:21:46.510 --> 00:21:48.070
there'll be another
quick turnaround.

00:21:48.070 --> 00:21:51.740
So the Google Maps team can
make that change digital

00:21:51.740 --> 00:21:52.980
and reach more people.

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:56.780
So if you're interested, feel
free to contact me via email.

00:21:56.780 --> 00:21:59.800
There's a very long
spreadsheet that I have.

00:21:59.800 --> 00:22:02.330
I'm more than happy to share
with anyone who would like.

00:22:02.330 --> 00:22:03.996
But there are plenty
of names out there.

00:22:03.996 --> 00:22:05.930
Just next time you're
out walking around,

00:22:05.930 --> 00:22:07.430
everything has a name.

00:22:07.430 --> 00:22:11.620
And some of those names
aren't appropriate anymore.

00:22:11.620 --> 00:22:13.190
And we know the
power of language

00:22:13.190 --> 00:22:14.890
and we know how we can hurt.

00:22:14.890 --> 00:22:16.500
But we also know
how it can help.

00:22:16.500 --> 00:22:18.166
So let's try to come
up with some better

00:22:18.166 --> 00:22:20.150
names for these places
that need to be changed.

